GCP Service Consumed API – Request Count (filtered)

timeSeriesQuery.timeSeriesQueryLanguage:
fetch consumed_api
| metric 'serviceruntime.googleapis.com/api/request_count'
| filter
    resource.project_id == '879579618750' && (metric.response_code != '200')
| align rate(1m)
| every 1m
| group_by [], [value_request_count_aggregate: aggregate(value.request_count)]

widgets.title: GCP Service Consumed API request sizes [COUNT]

timeSeriesQuery.timeSeriesQueryLanguage:
fetch consumed_api
| metric 'serviceruntime.googleapis.com/api/request_sizes'
| align delta(1m)
| every 1m
| group_by [], [row_count: row_count()]

widgets.title: GCP Service Consumed API – Request Latencies

timeSeriesQuery.timeSeriesQueryLanguage:
fetch consumed_api
| metric 'serviceruntime.googleapis.com/api/request_latencies'
| filter resource.project_id == '879579618750'
| align delta(1m)
| every 1m
| group_by [], [row_count: row_count()]

fetch datastore_request
| metric 'firestore.googleapis.com/api/request_count'
| filter resource.project_id == '879579618750'
| align rate(1m)
| every 1m

fetch datastore_request
| metric 'firestore.googleapis.com/api/request_count'
| filter
    resource.project_id == '879579618750'
    && (metric.api_method == 'RunQuery' && metric.response_code != 'OK')
| align rate(1m)
| every 1m
| group_by [], [row_count: row_count()]

fetch firestore_instance
| metric 'firestore.googleapis.com/network/active_connections'
| filter resource.project_id == '879579618750'
| group_by 1m, [value_active_connections_mean: mean(value.active_connections)]
| every 1m

fetch pubsub_subscription
| metric 'pubsub.googleapis.com/subscription/num_retained_acked_messages'
| filter
    resource.project_id == '879579618750'
    && (metadata.system_labels.topic_id == '')
| group_by 1m,
    [value_num_retained_acked_messages_mean:
       mean(value.num_retained_acked_messages)]
| every 1m
| group_by [],
    [value_num_retained_acked_messages_mean_aggregate:
       aggregate(value_num_retained_acked_messages_mean)]
